---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Ontario Home Value Consultation | Dongho Lee, Broker"
  description="Request a no-obligation Ontario home value and selling-readiness consultation with Dongho Lee, Broker."
>
  <section class="services-hero seller-lead-hero">
    <p class="page-kicker">For Ontario Homeowners</p>
    <h1>What could your home sell for?</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      A useful home-value conversation goes beyond an automated estimate. We review recent comparable sales,
      current competition, property condition, timing, and the likely costs of preparing for market.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="button primary" href="/contact/?source=home_value_consultation">Request a home-value consultation</a>
      <a class="button secondary" href="tel:14166258241">Call 416-625-8241</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process-steps" aria-label="Home value consultation steps">
    <article><span>01</span><h2>Property context</h2><p>Address, property type, improvements, condition, and your preferred timing.</p></article>
    <article><span>02</span><h2>Comparable evidence</h2><p>Relevant recent sales and active competition, with limitations explained.</p></article>
    <article><span>03</span><h2>Selling options</h2><p>Preparation priorities, possible timing, and next steps without a promise of outcome.</p></article>
  </section>

  <section class="services-cta">
    <div>
      <h2>Planning ahead is welcome.</h2>
      <p>Whether your timing is three months or two years away, the inquiry form records your timeframe so follow-up can stay appropriate.</p>
      <a class="button primary" href="/contact/?source=home_value_consultation">Start the conversation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
